SummaryEnglish: T-Buster and X-Buster are mercenaries ready to take on the world! On a peaceful Earth-day, space mercenary company EXIT summons them. The fateful battle to decide the team that will return to space begins! Meanwhile, the legendary Black Assault returns to Earth and so begins the collision between the space pirates and Buster mercenaries.
Aliases: Flaming Buster The Movie - The Return of the Black Assault
